t in this program- she has served for hundreds of hours during her high school years. Within the past year, she&#039;s spent nearly 100 hours volunteering- 70 of those hours being from non-profit organizations.\r\nThere&#039;s also things about Makayla that cannot be measured on paper, such as her inclusive personality, and willingness to help others. She is THE optimist, kind to everyone she meets, and has an unbelievably great work ethic.\r\nThank you for considering Makayla for this program.'),(2691,329,'_field_17','Mrs. Nicole Barnes\r\n(308) 874-4487\r\nnbarnes@lps.org\r\n\r\nMr. David Sharp\r\n(641) 799-0419\r\ndavid.sharp@indianhills.edu\r\n\r\nMs. Kelsie Bonow\r\n(402) 486-8563\r\nkelsie.bonow@tabitha.org'),(2692,329,'_field_4','7'),(2693,329,'_field_5',''),(2694,329,'_sub_id','329'),(2853,338,'_column_bigger','-1'),(2852,338,'_drop_shadow','-1'),(2698,182,'_edit_lock','1469715324:2'),(2699,260,'_edit_lock','1469715395:2'),(2700,270,'_edit_lock','1469715545:2'),(2701,269,'_edit_lock','1469715709:2'),(2702,327,'_edit_lock','1469755770:2'),(2851,338,'_featured_plan','-1'),(2705,64,'_theme_options_build','56f1b0d700aea'),(2706,331,'_form_id','1'),(2707,331,'_seq_num','11'),(2708,331,'_action','submit'),(2709,331,'_field_1','Hailey Dutton'),(2710,331,'_field_6','Lincoln East'),(2711,331,'_field_7','Junior '),(2712,331,'_field_8','Denette Russell'),(2713,331,'_field_9','11500 middle fork rd Lincoln ne '),(2714,331,'_field_10','(402) 875-0704'),(2715,331,'_field_11','Haileydutton@yahoo.com'),(2716,331,'_field_13','(402) 430-3836'),(2717,331,'_field_15','Denette.russell@yahoo.com'),(2718,331,'_field_12','(402) 326-9400'),(2719,331,'_field_2','Makdutton@yahoo.com'),(2720,331,'_field_3','Hailey is very driven in everything she does.  She is involved from soccer to volunteering at st. Elizabeth.  I&#039;ve seen her grow into an amazing young lady that will do great things!'),(2721,331,'_field_17','Lacy Helms LHelms@stez.org 402-219-7115, she is the director of volunte