ext month at Lincoln Southwest. She is a third year cheerleader, serving as captain last year, while also maintaining a 4.0 GPA. She volunteers as an assistant counselor at Camp Sonshine and as a leader for Vacation Bible School. This summer, she was selected for the CHI Health Summer camp, shadowing hospital personnel at CHI facilities in Lincoln. This was important to her as she is focused on working in pediatric oncology. \r\nShe also started her own online business when she was just 13 years old - Maci&#039;s Monograms. She started designing items for friends, but her success  quickly grew. Last year, she made close to 100 personalized water bottles for dancers in the Nutcracker.  \r\nMaci is a role model and leader, going the extra mile in everything she does.  I think she would be an incredible addition to the Lincoln Gold program. \r\n'),(6862,844,'_field_17','Whitney Hardesty 402-730-9334 wsahling@hotmail.com\r\n\r\nLisa Marks 402-450-5529 lisa@onyourmarks.com'),(6863,844,'_field_4','7'),(6864,844,'_field_5',''),(6865,844,'_sub_id','844'),(6866,845,'_form_id','1'),(6867,845,'_seq_num','29'),(6868,845,'_action','submit'),(6869,845,'_field_1','Caleigh Behrens '),(6870,845,'_field_6','Freeman High School '),(6871,845,'_field_7','11'),(6872,845,'_field_8','Spencer &amp; April Behrens '),(6873,845,'_field_9','16141 E Pickrell RD, Adams NE, 68301'),(6874,845,'_field_10','(402) 988-8497'),(6875,845,'_field_11','caleighbehrens10@gmail.com'),(6876,845,'_field_13','(402) 540-6452'),(6877,845,'_field_15','sb90317@gcsone.us'),(6878,845,'_field_12','(402) 540-6451'),(6879,845,'_field_2','aprilbehrens@gmail.com'),(6880,845,'_field_3','Caleigh is a very loving and hardworking girl. She participates in as many clubs/sports as she can at school, a few being cheer, volleyball, track, and FCA (fellowship of christian athletes). Caleigh dedicates most of her time to achieving her academic goals and volunteering at the local food pantry. She would love to become a part of the Li