 is an avid reader and writer.  During her time at home, Maddie maintains a book focused Instagram page and a book review website.  Her ability as a writer was recognized by an invitation to the Journalism Education Association Journalism Convention, which she attended in Washington DC, in November 2019.\r\n\r\nMaddie is an upstanding young woman who exhibits leadership ability in her school and community.  In addition to working hard for her community, particularly her faith-based community, Maddie has exhibited her organizational and time management abilities by excelling academically and socially. She is an outgoing, joyful young woman who works well with others and is an effective communicator and proficient writer. As a member of Lincoln G.O.L.D., I am confident Maddie will serve as an exemplary member and will be an asset to the organization. '),(11031,1119,'_field_17','Reference 1: Sheila Sievert\r\nPhone: 402-488-0931\r\nEmail: Shiela.Sievert@piusx.net\r\n\r\nReference 2: Nolan DeWispelare\r\nPhone: 402-488-0931\r\nEmail: Nolan.DeWispelare@piusx.net'),(11032,1119,'_field_4','7'),(11033,1119,'_field_5',''),(11034,1119,'_sub_id','1119'),(11035,1120,'_form_id','1'),(11036,1120,'_seq_num','60'),(11037,1120,'_action','submit'),(11038,1120,'_field_1','Michelle Kang'),(11039,1120,'_field_6','East High school'),(11040,1120,'_field_7','junior'),(11041,1120,'_field_8','Guobin Kang'),(11042,1120,'_field_9','2311 W ST APT. 11 '),(11043,1120,'_field_10','(402) 937-0176'),(11044,1120,'_field_11','michellemkang10@gmail.com'),(11045,1120,'_field_13','(402) 937-9579'),(11046,1120,'_field_15','guoxiaomei2009@gmail.com'),(11047,1120,'_field_12','(402) 580-3748'),(11048,1120,'_field_2','caklein888@gmail.com'),(11049,1120,'_field_3','Michelle is one of the kindest people that I know and she always has a great attitude towards everyone. I have done some volunteer work with her before through our school’s key club and she is always ready to work hard to help those in need. '),(110